{"id": "2070818493029847155", "url": "https://x.com/Energy_Tidbits/status/2070818493029847155", "text": "Bahrain says Iran launched drone attack on its territory.  No reports yet of damage.\n\nTimely story? ICYMI, 👇@WSJ report \"How Iran Devasted an American Naval Base [in Bahrain] - and caused a U.S. Recalculation\"   Thx @anikaaseth @shelbyholliday @deniseduana @milanczerny \n\n#oott", "created_at": "2026-06-27T10:36:17Z", "date": "2026-06-27", "hour": 10, "lang": "en", "source": "Twitter for iPhone", "retweets": 1, "replies": 1, "likes": 2, "quotes": 1, "views": 5700, "bookmarks": 2, "is_reply": false, "hashtags": ["oott"], "author": {"username": "Energy_Tidbits", "name": "Dan Tsubouchi", "followers": 15856, "blue_verified": true, "automated": false, "location": "Calgary, Alberta"}, "quoted": {"text": "When the Iranian missiles and drones came for the nerve center of America’s naval operations in the Middle East, some of them hit their mark. Satellite imagery reveals how much Iran damaged an American naval base in Bahrain. See the WSJ investigation: 🔗 https://t.co/sEfEXXx62b https://t.co/OBehhHjGcm", "author": "WSJ"}, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Iran", "Geopolitics"]}}
